list.name: Default
list.comment:
Make trignometry lut generation happen at compile time
- Remove TrigLookup * Move trig::TrigLookup::{sin, cos} to trig::{sin, cos} + Trig lookup table has 16K entries instead of 64K * Compresses the 4 quadrants into one * 64KB instead of 256KB in memory: better with the cache

task.summary:
Partial port to latest rs25/vocs implementation
- Temporarily disable decorator module, as Moore was removed + Temporarily re-add matcher module, removed in rs25/vocs
Split off main.rs into separate file, make into library

Minor tweaks to mirror changes to vocs
* Replace (i32, i32) with GlobalColumnPosition * Remove type / lifetimes from ColumnAssociation + Add HashSetMatcher to avoid type parameters, a stopgap until proper components in vocs

Change imports for vocs
* world::chunk -> indexed, storage -> root * Make Layer use LayerPacked and the new Palette
Fix typo in Knuth LCG docs

Make trignometry lut generation happen at compile time
- Remove TrigLookup * Move trig::TrigLookup::{sin, cos} to trig::{sin, cos} + Trig lookup table has 16K entries instead of 64K * Compresses the 4 quadrants into one * 64KB instead of 256KB in memory: better with the cache

Decoration support
+ Update to latest vocs * Split up main generation into 3 stages: initial gen, decoration, saving
